AUDIO: 'Just keep it up. &gt;&gt; Welcome back to the channel where we discuss the creative uses of AI and AI music has more than one player, you know. And some of these platforms fly under the radar and you never find out about their uniqueness. First up is this week\'s sponsor Melodity.ai or melody.ai.'

