VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'have your own lyrics and you have your own prompt, you can start the generation. But before you do that, you have a choice of models here. Recently, they added the latest Myureka model, which is version eight. The last time I played with it was 7.5. So, it\'ll be interesting to see how they\'ve improved'

